	  <div class="panel panel-default">
	    <div class="panel-heading">
	      <h4 class="panel-title">
	        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">
	          Where can I receive borrowed funds?
	        </a>
	      </h4>
	    </div>
	    <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
	      <div class="panel-body">
	      We have partnered with Coinfloor to allow borrowing on their exchange. However, we can arrange for funds to be received on other exchanges. If this interests you then please <a href="mailto:team@trademoremargin.com"> get in touch </a>. 
	      </div>
	    </div>
