	  <div class="panel panel-default">
	    <div class="panel-heading">
	      <h4 class="panel-title">
	        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFive">
	          What leverage do you offer?
	        </a>
	      </h4>
	    </div>
	    <div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
	      <div class="panel-body">
	      	New borrowers can received 2.5x leverage. Prior to receiving a loan, a borrower must deposit 40% of the loan’s principal (the Initial Margin Requirement). We may offer higher leverage to traders who consistently demonstrate strong performance and professionalism.  
	      </div>
	    </div>
	  </div>

	  <div class="panel panel-default">
	    <div class="panel-heading">
	      <h4 class="panel-title">
	        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSix">
	          Do you make margin calls?
	        </a>
	      </h4>
	    </div>
	    <div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
	      <div class="panel-body">
			Yes, if the price of bitcoin moves against a borrower we will request that they deposit more funds. If the borrower’s equity falls below 10% of the principal, we will sell fiat currency to protect the principal of the loan. 
	      </div>
	    </div>
	  </div>

	    <div class="panel panel-default">
	    <div class="panel-heading">
	      <h4 class="panel-title">
