	          How can I access my trading profits?
	        </a>
	      </h4>
	    </div>
	    <div id="collapseEight" class="panel-collapse collapse">
	      <div class="panel-body">
	      	To access trading profits, whether in bitcoin or fiat, you must make a request to TradeMore. If you satisfy the Initial Margin Requirement (see "What leverage do you offer?") then we will process your withdrawal request.
	      </div>
	    </div>
